query:
SELECT 
  pc.partnership_id,
  pc.child_id,
  CONCAT(child.first_name, ' ', child.last_name) as child_name,
  YEAR(child.birth_date) as child_birth_year,
  p.partner1_id,
  p.partner2_id,
  CONCAT(p1.first_name, ' ', p1.last_name) as partner1_name,
  YEAR(p1.birth_date) as partner1_birth_year,
  CONCAT(p2.first_name, ' ', p2.last_name) as partner2_name,
  YEAR(p2.birth_date) as partner2_birth_year
FROM partnership_children pc
JOIN people child ON pc.child_id = child.id
JOIN partnerships p ON pc.partnership_id = p.id
JOIN people p1 ON p.partner1_id = p1.id
JOIN people p2 ON p.partner2_id = p2.id
ORDER BY child.birth_date DESC
LIMIT 10;
